The cache downloads perfectly, until at 99% it stops and gives you the "Error Loading... Contact Staff!" error.. I also think there is an error in the unzipping because these are the files that get unzipped before the "Error Loading... Contact Staff!" error. Notice how it unpacked the zipped cache itself...
